40int EncoderSimulcastProxy::InitEncode(const VideoCodec* inst,
41 const VideoEncoder::Settings& settings) {
42 int ret = encoder_->InitEncode(inst, settings);
43 if (ret == WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_ERR_SIMULCAST_PARAMETERS_NOT_SUPPORTED) {
44 encoder_.reset(new SimulcastEncoderAdapter(factory_, video_format_));
45 if (callback_) {
46 encoder_->RegisterEncodeCompleteCallback(callback_);
47 }
48 ret = encoder_->InitEncode(inst, settings);
49 }
50 return ret;
51}
